structure.unit: LICENSING OF MOTOR VEHICLES, OPERATORS, AND TRAILERS

law.history: Repealed 1972 Ky. Acts ch. 123, sec. 2, effective June 16, 1972. -- Created 1968 Ky. Acts ch. 59, sec. 1.

metadata.catchline-at-repeal: Amateur radio licensees may attach plate showing call letters to license plate.
